content: I don't have personal preferences or emotions, so i don't have a favorite piece of street art. however, there are many famous street art pieces around the world that have gained widespread recognition and critical acclaim, such as banksy's works, including "girl with balloon" and "flower thrower". other notable works include the mural of che guevara in cuba by eduardo kobra, the colorful street art in wynwood, miami, and the extensive collection of murals in berlin, germany.
